07:47.425 --> 07:52.602
<i>MAN 1 (ON RADIO): Yeah, sure, it's possible
Lee Harvey Oswald didn't kill Kennedy.</i>

07:52.764 --> 07:54.812
<i>And frankly,
it's possible Jack Ruby...</i>

07:54.975 --> 07:59.276
<i>didn't kill Oswald. Look at those films,
you see this other guy hanging around.</i>

07:59.437 --> 08:02.281
<i>MAN 2 (ON RADIO): Are you
saying that Oswald is still alive?</i>

08:02.440 --> 08:06.365
<i>MAN 1: Well, no. Somebody who
looked like Lee Harvey Oswald.</i>

08:07.570 --> 08:09.493
She's singing.

08:10.573 --> 08:12.621
