(HORN HONKING RHYTHMICALLY)

10:34.509 --> 10:36.386
Ha-ha-ha! Look at him.

10:38.596 --> 10:40.690
Come on, keep up! Keep UP!

10:42.725 --> 10:45.023
- Can you swim, man?
- Ha-ha-ha!

10:45.186 --> 10:48.315
